text: Very rude woman boss. Scold customers in front of her religious figurines she is praying at the counter. Ppl should not patronize her unless really urgent. Let it close for good. She dont appreciate your business

The auntie got some sass in her and she scolded me when I was in pri school after I accidentally knocked a jar of sweets over. Low key got traumatised from it and didn't visit the shop since then. ITS BEEN 10+ YEARS BUT I WILL NEVER FORGET. 0/10
Quite well stocked with a variety of items. The aunty manning the counter is very loud like the aunty in Kung Fu Hustle, but if you look past her mannerisms she is actually quite likeable.
Almost complete minimart, you kind find your daily needs here. I especially liked the Yuzu drink and Japanese rice made available here. Auntie is friendly once you know her. Thanks!
The lady sitting at the counter is very rude.
